These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, coffee, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, skydiving, video-games, rock-climbing
1. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
3. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person drinking fanta##7
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | coffee | juice       | milk | fanta        |
| Hobby      | video-games  | skydiving | rock-climbing        | magic-tricks |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, turtle, lizard, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, water-polo, handball, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the person who's sport is handball and the owner of the lizard##7
2. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
3. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is water-polo##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | lizard | turtle       | goldfish         | rabbit     |
| Sport   | water-polo   | snowboarding | handball | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, disaster, horror, drama
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, electronic, reggae, r&b
1. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of r&b is somewhere between the fan of electronic and the fan of d&b##7
3. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the fan of d&b is somewhere between the fan of r&b and the person watching disaster movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | drama | horror | satire  |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | d&b  | r&b   | electronic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, filmmaking, baking, singing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, swimming, snowboarding, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's hobby is singing##7
3. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | sudoku | singing       | baking |
| Sport   | swimming      | basketball   | snowboarding | handball  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, woodworking, camping, chess
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, turkish, spanish, italian
1. the italian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
2. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the italian is somewhere between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is card-games##7
5. the italian is on the left of the spanish##1
6. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the italian##5
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping | card-games   | chess | woodworking |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | turkish | italian      | spanish |

