.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, tea, fanta
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, egyptian, japanese, malaysian
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the japanese##1
2. the japanese is the person drinking fanta##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
6. the malaysian is somewhere between the australian and the egyptian##7
7. the japanese is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | cola      | tea | fanta     |
| Nationality   | australian    | malaysian | egyptian   | japanese |

