.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, potato, plum, watermelon
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, japanese, pakistani, french
1. the polish is on the far left##1
2. the person eating potato is on the left of the japanese##1
3. the person eating watermelon is on the far left or far right##3
4. the french is somewhere between the person eating lettuce and the person eating plum##7
5. the pakistani is somewhere to the left of the person eating plum##5
6. the french is on the left or right of the pakistani##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | watermelon    | lettuce   | potato | plum  |
| Nationality   | polish | pakistani | french    | japanese |

