.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, turkish, australian, egyptian
4 different pets are kept: fish, ferret, lizard, hedgehog
1. the turkish is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
3. the egyptian is the owner of the lizard##1
4. the australian is somewhere between the egyptian and the indonesian##7
5. the turkish is on the left of the indonesian##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | egyptian | australian | turkish | indonesian |
| Pet           | lizard   | hedgehog    | fish       | ferret  |

