.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, architect, nurse, mechanic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, country, folk, funk
1. the dancer is not the fan of indie##6
2. the nurse is on the right of the dancer##1
3. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the dancer##3
4. the dancer is on the right of the fan of funk##1
5. the nurse is somewhere between the fan of funk and the architect##7
6. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | mechanic | dancer | nurse | architect |
| Music-Genre   | funk         | folk      | indie | country            |

