.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, scientific, superhero, comedy
4 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle, chinchilla, horse
1. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere between the person watching documentary movies and the owner of the horse##7
2. the person watching scientific movies is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
3. the owner of the turtle is not the person watching superhero movies##6
4. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
5. the person watching documentary movies is the owner of the ferret##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | comedy | scientific | superhero |
| Pet           | ferret    | turtle   | horse  | chinchilla      |

