2. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of classical##1
3. the fan of indie is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching family movies and the fan of indie##2
6. the fan of blues is somewhere between the fan of indie and the person watching family movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | western | spy | family | martial-arts   |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | blues      | classical      | d&b |

