2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere between the person driving the airplane and the person who's hobby is baking##7
7. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | woodworking | singing | board-games | baking |
| Transport   | airplane   | van      | snowmobile        | helicopter  |

