2. the fan of metal is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the fan of blues##7
3. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
4. the fan of blues is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the fan of salsa##5
6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the person drinking tea is the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | juice   | hot-chocolate | tea | iced-tea   |
| Music-Genre   | funk | blues   | metal | salsa |

