3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
5. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
6. the person driving the ship is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage    | cola   | water  | sprite  | coffee |
| Transport   | bus | motorbike | boat | ship    |

