.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, pony, horse, hedgehog
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, van, tram, helicopter
1. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the person driving the taxi and the owner of the pony##7
2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
5. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | pony    | horse | hedgehog     | turtle |
| Transport   | tram | helicopter  | van | taxi |

 